data.description: Charming ranch with a covered front porch with porch swing, new HVAC, new roof, new water heater, freshly insulated, and an in-ground saltwater pool! This one-story home has a large kitchen with a breakfast area with bay windows, along with a formal dining room. Enjoy more bay windows in the primary suite, along with a separate shower and tub. This home has a flex room leading to a large deck overlooking a huge fenced backyard complete with an in-ground salt-water pool, outbuilding storage, and a playhouse. Donat forget to check out the awesome park across the street from this quiet neighborhood - J.P. Moseley Park! Itas the perfect place for a morning jog or a day at the playground. NO HOA No rental restrictions. Pool serviced and winterized 1 Nov 2023 by Moore Pools
